Question: The right image shows seals piled on multiple floating platforms, and the left image includes an upright seal in an uncrowded foreground.

Reference Answer: False

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image show an upright seal in an uncrowded foreground?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image show seals piled on multiple floating platforms?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
